# ── 1. PROJECT IDENTITY ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

You are building FC Trader: a fully automated trading bot for the EA Sports
FC 26 Companion Android app. It runs inside Docker, spins up a headless
Android emulator via AVD, installs the FC Companion APK, logs into EA,
and executes three trading strategies (Sniper, Mass Bidder, Chemistry Style
Trader) driven by a real-time market calendar and external market intelligence
scraped from FUTWIZ, FUTBIN, and FUT.GG.

The project has TWO Docker services:
  1. fc-trader   — Python bot + Android emulator (heavy, KVM-backed)
  2. intel       — Lightweight Python sidecar scraping market data

They share a single named Docker volume (shared-data) containing a SQLite DB.


